Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:02.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢業…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.27,0:00:05.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都在逐漸改變
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.74,0:00:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對教給我各種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.00,0:00:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與我相遇的所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.23,0:00:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要由衷地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.55,0:00:14.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說聲謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.15,0:00:17.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之類的…超級害羞 我說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.05,0:00:33.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 對於諸位順利完成了所有課程的畢業生們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望你們能以從這所歷史悠久的學校畢業為榮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:43.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我期待你們能時時準備著向未來展翅翱翔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:52.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 愛麗絲前輩走過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:54.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.86,0:00:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳快去說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.24,0:00:57.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？我…我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.75,0:01:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那個…愛麗絲前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.83,0:01:04.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜妳順利畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.82,0:01:06.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如…如果可以的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.77,0:01:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能把妳制服的第二顆紐扣給我們嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:17.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.11,0:01:19.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 太謝謝妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.04,0:01:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.57,0:01:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.82,0:01:25.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.43,0:01:28.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我也一直是妳的崇拜者
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.36,0:01:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.03,0:01:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 真狡猾 我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.43,0:01:30.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級嚇人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.83,0:01:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好像沒告訴妳們今天是畢業典禮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.45,0:01:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別小看了畢業於相同學校的前輩哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.65,0:01:57.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜妳順利畢業 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.45,0:02:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 謝謝二位前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:09.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:15.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今年夏天 愛麗絲終於從中學畢業了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.99,0:03:10.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像平常一樣走路嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.66,0:03:12.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也覺得應該那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是這是中學時期最後的挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.64,0:03:17.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我必須做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.12,0:03:22.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 雅典娜前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小後輩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.89,0:03:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒走可是失敗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.23,0:03:45.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,關於那個的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,倒是超級No problem
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.96,0:03:49.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有雅典娜前輩在的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.05,0:03:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間就是靜止的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:02.59,TITLE,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)\pos(433,290)\blur9\be1\fsp2}那陣 橙色和風之中…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.01,0:04:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳳尾舟 要通過了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:09.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.99,0:04:12.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小後輩 非常有幹勁呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.88,0:04:14.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對 非常地
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:17.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為以前在學校耽誤了的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以後都能用來跟前輩們一起練習了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.20,0:04:22.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.25,0:04:26.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我…超級高興
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.19,0:04:31.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常好！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:34.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我們也向著正式領航員 Let's go！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.65,0:04:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,燈里 亞利亞社長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.91,0:04:38.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是發聲練習哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.31,0:04:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是 是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.26,0:04:42.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳳尾舟 要通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.90,0:04:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那愛麗絲從學校畢業後
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.32,0:04:52.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在非常有幹勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.04,0:04:53.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我現在感覺自己超級能幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:04:59.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然自己也感覺很不可思議
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是覺得現在無論做什麼都能非常順利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘛社長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.55,0:05:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊 來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:14.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.08,0:05:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.69,0:05:35.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們明天去野餐好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.67,0:05:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次 一定要去成
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.30,0:06:04.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 妳在做什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.70,0:06:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,便當的準備都完成了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:21.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級完美呢 雅典娜前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.41,0:06:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:33.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一天我來扮演客人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.24,0:06:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲來扮演領航員帶我遊覽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.09,0:06:47.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很有趣的主意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:49.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接受這個建議
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那雅典娜前輩現在開始就是我重要的客人了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.06,0:06:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 請多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.12,0:07:02.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位客人 請握住我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.46,0:07:10.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.36,0:07:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲的笑容變得很自然了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.57,0:07:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思 我們好像是初次見面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.68,0:07:28.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.97,0:07:39.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實我每天都在跟能夠給我最棒的笑容的前輩們練習
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.51,0:08:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這一座是僅憑一個橋拱就橫跨了48米大運河的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里亞托橋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.22,0:08:02.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(427,440)\fs20}Ponte di Rialto
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這周圍與聖馬可廣場不同
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.08,0:08:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,商店 市場 酒店和居民區混雜在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:14.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡可以感受到新威尼斯真實的民間生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.73,0:08:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可說是第二個城鎮中心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領航員小姐的觀光解說
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.66,0:08:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常清晰易懂呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.34,0:08:29.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我每天都被滿口禁止的前輩重點培訓呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.36,0:08:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 客人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來您想參觀什麼地方呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果您有想要參觀的景點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請儘管吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:49.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.64,0:08:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我就恭敬不如從命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.25,0:09:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從這裡開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.06,0:09:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前面是一片田園地帶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.50,0:09:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與這座著名的港口城市有著迥異的風景
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.26,0:09:13.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請您享受新威尼斯的另一種風情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.69,0:09:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.07,0:09:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.50,0:09:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.82,0:09:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.18,0:09:46.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請各位慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(427,440)\fs20}Ciao
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳們好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(427,440)\fs20}Buon giorno
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.16,0:09:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hi～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 您很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:10:00.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.83,0:10:15.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 您想再來杯茶嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:18.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝 不過不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:24.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真是個野餐的好日子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.64,0:10:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領航員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:43.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.44,0:10:45.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.77,0:10:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.80,0:11:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大叔 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:10.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:15.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 現在剛好在下行中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.72,0:11:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再稍微等一會就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.62,0:11:18.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？領航員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…看上去這麼不可靠嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.00,0:11:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 非常可靠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.32,0:12:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天辛苦妳了 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.64,0:12:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:06.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個水上電梯到達頂部之前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把工作模式切換掉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.23,0:12:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.78,0:12:12.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.17,0:12:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.62,0:12:18.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經做什麼都沒問題了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.03,0:12:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝妳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的確認為在跟前輩們開始練習後
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.24,0:12:30.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的技術和觀光解說是變得有模有樣了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:34.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,船歌就…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.17,0:12:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本來聲音很小
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.81,0:12:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且也不太擅長唱歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以不知道自己有沒有放開聲音…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.87,0:12:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不知道自己有沒有走調…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.73,0:12:51.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越是覺得自己必須學好船歌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:55.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,腦袋裡就越是一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.92,0:13:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己覺得唱得很辛苦的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽眾自然也會聽得很難受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.70,0:13:14.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唱歌的技巧當然不可或缺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但最重要的是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.82,0:13:20.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡唱歌這種心情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:24.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡…唱歌…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲的歌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.42,0:13:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果連愛麗絲自己都不喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.33,0:13:34.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那還有誰會去喜歡呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.54,0:13:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:54.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領航員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.05,0:13:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的地就在眼前了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:01.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.33,0:14:23.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妳知道嗎？領航員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說在這顆星球的地表上充滿海水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.90,0:14:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被稱為AQUA之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.19,0:14:36.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整個世界都是橙色的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.30,0:14:39.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許正因為如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.32,0:14:43.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在世界被染上橙色的短短這段時間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.98,0:14:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這些住在水星的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.02,0:14:49.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都會覺得非常眷戀 非常感懷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.08,0:14:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡蘊藏著…我們的永遠一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.09,0:15:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.76,0:15:25.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.82,0:15:31.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是燈里前輩和藍華前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.84,0:15:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有剛才管理水上電梯的大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.68,0:15:42.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,後面的是公司的高層人員和鳳尾舟協會的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:49.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.97,0:15:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天一天真是太感謝妳了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:15:59.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領航員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.42,0:16:03.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在最後能請妳唱首歌嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,領航員小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.25,0:16:25.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人 您知道名揚水星的水之三大精靈嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.89,0:16:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.08,0:16:33.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別看我這樣 我也是其中那位
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被稱為風之精靈的領航員的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(398,440)\fs20}Seiren
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.50,0:16:37.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得意弟子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.61,0:19:02.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.25,0:19:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我過去不擅長唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.72,0:19:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我小時候最喜歡的就是唱歌了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.31,0:19:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,客人的話讓我回想起了那時的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.02,0:19:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公司一直在等著妳從中學畢業
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,划船的技術非常完美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.57,0:20:03.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都讓人擔心的觀光解說和客人的接待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.19,0:20:05.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後連船歌都
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在今天的考試裡展現出了顯著的進步
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.14,0:20:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前輩…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:29.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對於擔負了水上領航協會下一代重任的妳
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:33.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鳳尾舟協會給予了非常高的評價
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.17,0:20:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,並且懷著強烈的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.40,0:20:37.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做出了前所未有的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.21,0:20:39.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果斷的決定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜妳 愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.46,0:20:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 橙星公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:21:00.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天開始 妳就是正式領航員了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.40,0:21:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,橙星…公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.38,0:21:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.23,0:21:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.53,0:21:24.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.23,0:21:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雅典娜前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.33,0:21:32.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.66,0:21:46.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.71,0:21:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,二位前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.80,0:21:50.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.08,0:21:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.36,0:21:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.36,0:21:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小後輩～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.46,0:21:59.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.86,0:22:03.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:07.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝前輩…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.59,0:22:16.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.84,0:22:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鐫刻在水星歷史上的領航員的光輝歷程中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:23.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又誕生了前所未有的跳級成為正式領航員的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:26.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.78,0:22:28.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲小姐真的好厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.14,0:22:31.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有點崇拜她了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:33.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜妳 愛麗絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.00,0:24:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛麗絲成為正式領航員了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,0:24:09.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我早就有這種預感了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.53,0:24:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我超級超級緊張…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.28,0:24:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種時候就要讓心情放鬆～
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.05,0:24:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.82,0:24:17.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那份 賞月之夜的心動…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.50,0:24:19.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來 請握住我的手
